## 🔴 高危安全问题 (P1 - 尽快修复)

### 2. 权限绕过模式风险 🔴

**问题描述**: 
`bypassPermissions` 模式在多个地方被使用，允许 AI Agent 完全控制系统

**证据**:
```typescript
// src/main.ts:129
permissionMode: 'bypassPermissions',

// src/base-agent.ts:43
protected permissionMode: PermissionMode = 'acceptEdits';
```

**风险等级**: 🔴 **高危**

**影响**:
- AI Agent 可以执行任意命令
- 可以修改、删除任何文件
- 可能导致系统被破坏
- 在自主迭代模式下风险更高

**修复建议**:

```typescript
// ✅ 实现安全的权限管理
export class SecurePermissionManager {
  private allowedPaths: Set<string>;
  private blockedCommands: Set<string>;
  private auditLog: AuditLogger;

  constructor() {
    // 只允许操作项目目录
    this.allowedPaths = new Set([
      process.cwd(),  // 项目根目录
      '/tmp/ai-dev-team',  // 临时目录
    ]);

    // 阻止危险命令
    this.blockedCommands = new Set([
      'rm -rf /',
      'mkfs',
      'dd if=',
      'chmod 000',
      '> /dev/sda',
    ]);

    this.auditLog = new AuditLogger();
  }

  /**
   * 验证操作是否被允许
   */
  validateOperation(operation: string, target?: string): boolean {
    // 检查是否包含危险命令
    for (const blocked of this.blockedCommands) {
      if (operation.includes(blocked)) {
        this.auditLog.log('BLOCKED', { operation, reason: 'Dangerous command' });
        return false;
      }
    }

    // 检查目标路径是否在允许范围内
    if (target) {
      const targetPath = path.resolve(target);
      const isAllowed = Array.from(this.allowedPaths).some(allowed => 
        targetPath.startsWith(allowed)
      );

      if (!isAllowed) {
        this.auditLog.log('BLOCKED', { operation, target, reason: 'Path not allowed' });
        return false;
      }
    }

    this.auditLog.log('ALLOWED', { operation, target });
    return true;
  }
}

// ✅ 在 BaseAgent 中使用安全权限管理
export abstract class BaseAgent {
  private permissionManager: SecurePermissionManager;

  constructor(config: AgentConfig) {
    this.permissionManager = new SecurePermissionManager();
    // ...
  }

  async *execute(prompt: string): AsyncGenerator<any> {
    // 在执行前验证所有操作
    for await (const message of query({...})) {
      if (message.type === 'toolUse') {
        const { tool, input } = message;

        // 验证工具使用
        if (!this.permissionManager.validateOperation(tool, input?.path)) {
          throw new SecurityError(`Operation not allowed: ${tool}`);
        }
      }

      yield message;
    }
  }
}
```

